            <section xml:id="group__IL__POLLER_1ga90aa41e8a0ff21af9d077e522cefb205">
                <title>IL_EXPORT int il_poller_configure (il_poller_t *poller, unsigned int t_s, size_t buf_sz)</title> <emphasis>Configure poller parameters.</emphasis>
                
<para><formalpara><title>Note: </title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>The maximum stable polling rate is ~500 Hz (2 ms) for a single register when the servo is enabled.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>The buffer size must be set according to your application needs. It should be large enough so that it can store all samples collected between subsequent calls to <computeroutput>il_poller_data_get</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</formalpara>

                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters                        </title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <colspec colwidth="1*"/>
                        <colspec colwidth="4*"/>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>poller</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>Poller instance. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>t_s</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>Sampling period (ms). </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>buf_sz</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>Buffer size.</para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                <formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>0 on success, error code otherwise. </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
